00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:29,200
of making science understandable to everyone, which

264
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:31,680
brings us to the issue of populism, which has also

265
00:14:31,680 --> 00:14:36,800
gotten a very complicated politically in the past year.

266
00:14:36,800 --> 00:14:42,200
And I think that I guess the biggest difference

267
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:45,480
between, or at least, that's the way it seemed to me

