272
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:07,920
Scientists are interested in figuring things out.

273
00:15:07,920 --> 00:15:11,960
And so this idea has arisen that artists can then

274
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:17,440
be kind of brought in to take the figuring out and explain it.

275
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:22,080
