00:21:00,080 --> 00:21:01,920
They include irony.

361
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:05,440
They include cultural critique, et cetera.

362
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:08,680
And you're not going to do that in science.

363
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:21,760
OK, so I think that the question of comfortability between disciplines

