387
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:51,880
Every medium in art is a technology, painting is a technology,

388
00:22:51,880 --> 00:22:54,240
sculptures the technology.

389
00:22:54,240 --> 00:22:57,320
Books were a technology that were cutting edge

390
00:22:57,320 --> 00:22:59,920
at the time that they were introduced.

391
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:03,360
