00:26:05,600 --> 00:26:10,600
Have huge implications on the gallery system.

432
00:26:10,600 --> 00:26:14,720
Perhaps galleries wouldn't be necessary in a situation like that.

433
00:26:14,720 --> 00:26:18,480
You could just print out a version of the painting and live with it for a while.

434
00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:21,040
And if you wanted to buy the real one, you could.

