00:28:12,880 --> 00:28:14,800
That would be interesting to see.

458
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:19,600
I think in the long run, historically, it is ironic because it does contradict itself.

459
00:28:19,600 --> 00:28:21,600
Well, there's also junk science.

