00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:52,240
And that's great, and that's to its benefit.

466
00:28:52,240 --> 00:28:55,840
We don't have to throw out Leonardo's artwork ever.

467
00:28:55,840 --> 00:29:02,360
That's a real clear distinction, I think it's important and absolutely true.

468
00:29:02,360 --> 00:29:11,520
So what do we learn from that is part of the question of the boundary, I think.

469
00:29:11,520 --> 00:29:13,960
There's clear boundary on that point.

